    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"ariadne-entry\"><p><strong>Source:</strong> Ariadne's Book of Legends - Alpha v1.2, p. 111.</p><p>White Flame</p><p>Infusion, Ichimonji</p><p>Weapon: Any Classes: Fighter, Monk, Paladin Channeling Time: 1 bonus action Base LP Cost: 0 LP Range: Self Duration: Concentration, up to 1 minute</p><p>You infuse your next weapon attack, unarmed strike, or Multiplier Attack with the white flame of your soul, burning with a light that strikes deeper than flesh. For the duration, the next weapon attack or unarmed strike you make deals soul damage instead of its normal damage type.</p></div>",
